verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
Holy, Holy, Holy Lord God of hosts.
Holy, Holy, Holy Lord God of hosts.
Heaven and earth are full, full of your glory.
Hosanna in the highest.
Hosanna in the highest.

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
Blessed, blessed, blessed is He
who comes in the name of the Lord.
Blessed, blessed, blessed is He
who comes in the name of the Lord.
Heaven and earth are full, full of your glory.

verse.name: v3
verse.lines:
Hosanna in the highest.
Hosanna in the highest.
Hosanna in the highest.
